This paper focuses on the degrees of freedom of a holographic MIMO channel, which involves the propagation of electromagnetic waves. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM), as well as signal processing (cs.SI) and networking (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper discusses the physical properties of the channel, which could fall under the category of physics (cs.PH).
